    /// `Set.union`'s own O((n+m) log n) fast path (production-hardening
    /// PR-it828, the SIXTH instance of the naive-O(n^2)-collection-algorithm
    /// bug class): confirms BigInt/SizedInt/F32 coverage, Rational exclusion,
